<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Screencast&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://digitalmedia.oreilly.com/pub/a/oreilly/digitalmedia/2005/11/16/what-is-screencasting.html?page=1" class="external text" title="http://digitalmedia.oreilly.com/pub/a/oreilly/digitalmedia/2005/11/16/what-is-screencasting.html?page=1" rel="nofollow">O'Reilly Digital Media: What Is Screencasting, a screencasting guide by Jon Udell</a></li>
<li><a href="http://weblog.infoworld.com/udell/2005/02/21.html" class="external text" title="http://weblog.infoworld.com/udell/2005/02/21.html" rel="nofollow">All About ScreenCasting - Jon Udell of InfoWorld</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.screencam.biz/forum/index.php?topic=4.0" class="external text" title="http://www.screencam.biz/forum/index.php?topic=4.0" rel="nofollow">Good ScreenCasting Tips and Tricks Sheet</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.digital-web.com/articles/mac_screencast_capturing/" class="external text" title="http://www.digital-web.com/articles/mac_screencast_capturing/" rel="nofollow">Capturing Screencasts on a Mac</a> - Complete overview of screencasting on the Mac, including workflow, software, and editing.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.teachmac.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.teachmac.com/" rel="nofollow">TeachMac &amp; TeachIT</a> - Example of use of screencast technology for CBT.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.freecharity.org.uk/2007/04/12/the-secret-to-screencasting-with-ubuntu-and-free-software/" class="external text" title="http://www.freecharity.org.uk/2007/04/12/the-secret-to-screencasting-with-ubuntu-and-free-software/" rel="nofollow">The Secret to Screencasting with Ubuntu and Free Software</a> - Details one method to create screencasts using only <a href="/wiki/Free_Software" title="Free Software" class="mw-redirect">Free Software</a>.</li>
</ul>
